About Us
.entry-header
Established in 2012
Island Girl Ponte Vedra Beach is a locally owned cigar lounge with a full bar and outside seating. Thanks to the owners, Rosa & Mark, Island Girl is a relaxed environment suitable for enjoying a fine cigar and good conversation. We invite you to enjoy a little of island life while you’re here and become part of the family!
Cigars
We have over 600 facings of premium cigars from countries like- Nicaragua, Dominican Republic, Honduras and many more.
Bar
Full liquor bar including, over 40 different scotches and bourbon, 20 different beers on tap and wine picked to pair perfectly with all variety of cigars.
Family
We’re more than just smiling faces, we are family, welcoming everyone with open arms. Visit once or all the time, you can always feel at home with your Island Family.
.entry-content
